# Memory allocator algorithm selection
# 通过 Kconfig 宏在 FSC、TLSF、bestfit_little、bestfit 之间切换。
# 以算法名命名，便于后续新增 allocator。
menu "MM Modules Configuration"

config OS_MEM_ARITH_TLSF
    bool "Use TLSF memory allocator"
    default n
    help
      Select y to use the TLSF (Two-Level Segregated Fit) memory allocator
      instead of the default UniProton FSC allocator. The TLSF algorithm
      source is kept in the allocator directory; a thin adaptation shim +
      glue layer is added under src/mem/tlsf/. When enabled, the FSC
      implementation (src/mem/fsc/prt_fscmem.c) is excluded from the build
      and litelibc's malloc_usable_size.c is replaced by the TLSF glue
      implementation.

config OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT_LITTLE
    bool "Use bestfit_little memory allocator"
    default n
    depends on !OS_MEM_ARITH_TLSF && !OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT
    help
      Select y to use the bestfit_little dynamic memory allocator. The
      allocator is integrated as an algorithm peer of FSC/TLSF through the
      existing UniProton memory dispatch table.

config OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT
    bool "Use bestfit memory allocator"
    default n
    depends on !OS_MEM_ARITH_TLSF && !OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT_LITTLE
    help
      Select y to use the full bestfit dynamic memory allocator. The
      allocator is integrated as an algorithm peer of FSC/TLSF through the
      existing UniProton memory dispatch table.

config OS_MEM_SLAB_EXTENTION
    bool "Enable slab extension for bestfit allocators"
    default n
    depends on OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT_LITTLE || OS_MEM_ARITH_BESTFIT
    help
      Enable the slab small-block cache in front of bestfit_little or bestfit.
      Slab is an extension of the selected bestfit heap path, not an independent
      UniProton memory algorithm.

config OS_MEM_SLAB_AUTO_EXPANSION_MODE
    bool "Enable slab auto expansion mode"
    default n
    depends on OS_MEM_SLAB_EXTENTION
    help
      Allow the slab extension to allocate additional buckets from the backing
      bestfit heap.

endmenu
